features.description: The SearchNEU team is excited to announce a major update to the platform, featuring a completely redesigned user interface, fully functional notifications, and a more responsive design for smoother performance across all devices. This release focuses on quality-of-life improvements to make your search experience faster, cleaner, and more intuitive than ever.
